data.description: Beautiful newly renovated 4 Bed, 2 bath home! This home features four spacious bedrooms, two bedrooms with walk in closets, two full baths with tile floors and bathtub. The kitchen features quartz countertops, brand new backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. Resurfaced hard wood floors, tray ceilings, living and dining room on the first floor. The second floor has brand new wall to wall carpet. New furnace, New hot water heater, gas stove and gas heat. Home has a cozy yard for gatherings. Parking in rear as well as street parking available. Conveniently located near Taunton Green, shops, and restaurants. Easy access to Route 24. Move In Ready! Welcome home! No offers accepted until after the open house.  Open House January 13th 6-7:30pm, January 14th 2:15pm-3:45pm and January 15th 11am-12:30pm!
